---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
title="Professional Cleaning Checklist"
description="Typical tasks included in professional cleaning services."
canonicalPath="/cleaning-checklist"
>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">

    <h1>Professional Cleaning Checklist</h1>

    <p class="hero-intro">
      Professional cleaning services usually follow a structured checklist to
      ensure consistent and thorough results across every room of the property.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="grid grid-2">

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Kitchen Cleaning</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Worktops and surfaces cleaned</li>
          <li>Sinks and taps cleaned</li>
          <li>Appliance exteriors wiped</li>
          <li>Cupboard fronts cleaned</li>
          <li>Floors vacuumed and mopped</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Bathroom Cleaning</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Toilet sanitised</li>
          <li>Shower and bath cleaned</li>
          <li>Sinks and taps polished</li>
          <li>Mirrors wiped</li>
          <li>Bathroom floors cleaned</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Living Areas</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Dusting surfaces and furniture</li>
          <li>Vacuuming carpets and rugs</li>
          <li>Mopping hard floors</li>
          <li>Light switches and handles wiped</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Bedrooms</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Dusting surfaces</li>
          <li>Vacuuming carpets</li>
          <li>Cleaning mirrors and glass surfaces</li>
          <li>General room tidying</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section section-soft">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Cleaning Scope</h2>

    <p class="section-intro">
      The exact tasks included in a cleaning service can vary depending on the
      type of service requested, property size and the condition of the property.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-2">

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Standard Cleaning</h3>
        <p>
          Regular cleaning typically focuses on maintaining cleanliness across
          kitchens, bathrooms, living areas and bedrooms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Deep Cleaning</h3>
        <p>
          Deep cleaning services involve additional attention to areas that are
          not normally covered during routine cleaning visits.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>End of Tenancy Cleaning</h3>
        <p>
          Tenancy cleaning follows stricter inspection standards designed to
          prepare a property for landlord or letting agent inspection.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>After Builders Cleaning</h3>
        <p>
          After builders cleaning focuses on removing construction dust,
          residue and renovation debris from the property.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section section-cta">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Request a Cleaning Quote</h2>

    <p>
      If you need professional cleaning services, you can request a quote
      through the CamCleans platform.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a class="button" href="/quote">Get a Quote</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>